  "remarks": "Alexey Belyaev is the General Director of JSC “Sarapul Electric Generator Plant” (SEGZ), a Russian company manufacturing power generation, control and protection systems, equipment for military aircraft and helicopters, and components for rocket technology. JSC SEGZ produces critical parts for Russian long-range aircraft. The company participates in the fulfilment of the Russian State defence order, with over half of its revenue derived from military contracts.",
